@ozzWANTED This is still working correctly in Core, what is not working correctly is your combination of arguments. Unless you are planning on creating your own custom meta capabilities setting <code>map_meta_cap</code> to <code>false</code> is essentially removing all the <code>post</code> capabilities. Therefore, you either need to set <code>map_meta_cap</code> to <code>true</code> or roll out your own capabilities.
